Class SystemAdapter

All Implemented Interfaces:
ExpandableListAdapter, HeterogeneousExpandableList
Deprecated. 

public class SystemAdapter
extends BaseExpandableListAdapter

Adapter for listview in system tab of administration app. Provides data for monitored system activities, grouped by related system calls which are used to update the values for the monitored metrics. The first child of each group is the administration row, which allows the user to enable/disable monitoring of the metric, and specify a frequency.

This adapter maintains an ArrayList of the current monitored values for all metrics, which are updated directly by the metric monitoring agent for efficiency.

Author:
darts
